text: Jennifer Wood (born 4 August 1972) is a Canadian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Edmonton Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1991 Pan American Games
